text: Yalli koros edde tanih tan umaane baxxaqqa edde haa ceelallo yoogore : naqasuy tu abam duude waa kee aka numuy culul baxah yaniy calaaalih yan rizqhiy meqe kah neceey woo rizqhi qellisak ayballayuk yacee maay missowtaah? ma missowta, fayla dubuk Yalli le tannah tan baxxaqqa neh abe waqdi, wonna hinnay keenik maggo mari faylaa kee niqmoota Yalli lem mayaaxiga
